subproject.description: This project will facilitate the development of UNDP Programmes and projects and the growth of Programme clusters, by providing funds for the use of: conducting researches and partners’/target group needs assessments, contracting local and international consultants, local and regional travel, bringing in UNDP Policy Advisors as necessary for the development and elaboration of project documents for the UNDP Montenegro Office
